{"word":"G3707 - ὁρατός - horatós - hor-at-os' - Visible","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁρατός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">horatós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hor-at-os'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Visible</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காணப்படுகிறவைகளுமான"},{"paragraph":"visible, open to view"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3708 - ὁράω - horáō - hor-ah'-o/3708\">G3708</a>; <i>gazed at</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>capable of being seen:</i> - visible.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2300/2300\">G2300</a>, <a href=\"#/G2334/2334\">G2334</a>, <a href=\"#/G2529/2529\">G2529</a>, <a href=\"#/G3705/3705\">G3705</a>, <a href=\"#/G3706/3706\">G3706</a>, <a href=\"#/G3707/3707\">G3707</a>, <a href=\"#/G3708/3708\">G3708</a>, <a href=\"#/G4308/4308\">G4308</a>, <a href=\"#/G517/517\">G517</a>"}]}